IN RE: CONDEMNATION BY SUNOCO PIPELINE L.P. of Permanent and Temporary Rights of Way and Easements for the Transportation of Ethane, Propane, Liquid Petroleum Gas, and other Petroleum Products in Thornbury Township, Delaware County, Pennsylvania, over the Lands of Traymore Investment Partners, L.P. ORDER
